item.title: How do i do this?
item.dc:creator: @Kalphiter Kalphiter
item.description:
@Kalphiter wrote:

Your wearing Silab items while you are on Mopar. If you are wearing those, don’t click on the “equip” interface or it will freeze. Now, you could try changing what you start with. Go into player.java and search for “playerEquipment[playerHat]”. Now, it will look like this: playerEquipment[playerHat]=14096; playerEquipment[playerCape]=14095; playerEquipment[playerAmulet]=6585; playerEquipment[playerChest]=14512; playerEquipment[playerShield]=13601; playerEquipment[playerLegs]=14511; playerEquipment[playerHands]=7462; playerEquipment[playerFeet]=15352; playerEquipment[playerRing]=-1; playerEquipment[playerArrows]=-1; playerEquipment[playerWeapon]=4151;. All those numbers are IDs. Change them accordingly to any non-Silab item.
